{
  "id": "adv_main_01_19_05",
  "title": "星見編4章20話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "…………！　夢？\n午前、二時……俺、眠ってたのか？　でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh! It was a dream?\nIt’s 2… in the morning… Was I asleep? But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "「待ってる」って、麻奈は言った……\nどこで？　ここじゃないとすると、どこだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana said she’ll be waiting…\nWhere? If not here‚ then where?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.566666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "寮か？　事務所か？　ステージ……いや、事故に遭った\nあの現場……違う。もっとあるはずだ……もしかして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The dorm? The office? On stage? No… the scene of the accident?\nNo… There’s got to be somewhere else. Just maybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 33.599999999999994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（一心不乱に走った。『その場所』に向かって）\n（脳裏に甦る。麻奈が俺に、マネージャーを頼んだあの日）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I run with everything I have. I run to “the place.”)\n(The past comes alive again. The day Mana asked me to be her manager.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.66666666666668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3.552713678800501e-11,
          "startTime": 34.6666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 46.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 46.349999999999994
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 46.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "本当にいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re really okay with it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.43333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "嫌だって言ってほしいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you want me to say no?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.93333338101704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 52.50641730626423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳じゃないけど……\nきっと大変だよ。沢山嫌なこととかあるかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not exactly…\nIt’s going to be a lot of hard work. Probably a lot of stuff you’ll hate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.173083972930904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ\nっていうか、分かってて誘ったんだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that.\nI mean‚ you asked me‚ knowing that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.90641730626423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 64.07308397286423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0730839729309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺がやるって言ったんだから、それでいいだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I said I’d do it. Isn’t that good enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.03975063959754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 68.76873027483622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（不機嫌そうな俺を見て、麻奈は心の底から）\n（嬉しそうに笑った。そして、言ったのだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana looked at my frowning face‚ and she smiled‚)\n(with all her heart. Then‚ she said this to me…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1687302748362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 76.80206360816952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "絶対、後悔させないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t let you ever regret it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.80206360816952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "大変なことも沢山あるかもしれないけど\nマネージャーやって良かったって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There might be lots of hard times ahead‚\nbut you’ll be happy to be my manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.32036299705501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 85.7536963303883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、OKして良かったって\n絶対に思ってもらえるようにするから。命に代えても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll be glad you said yes when I asked you.\nI promise I’ll make it so you’ll feel that way. I swear it on my life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 94.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 99.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（あれは、本気だったんだ。本当にそう思ってたんだ）\n（死ぬまで、いや死んでからもずっとそう思ってたんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She was serious. She genuinely felt that way.)\n(Until the day she died… no‚ even in death‚ she still felt that way.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 106.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 106.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（夜中の町を走り抜け、『その場所』に辿り着く）\n（高校時代、俺と麻奈がいた教室だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I run through the dark town and arrive at “the place.”)\n(Our classroom in high school.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 114.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 115.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "よく、分かったね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guessed correctly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "クイズはやめてくれよ。散々考えたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop quizzing me. I racked my brain to figure it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 123.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに難しいクイズじゃないと思うけど……\nでも、{user}くん鈍いからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think it was a very challenging quiz.\nBut you are kind of dense‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく走ってきたのに、文句？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I ran all the way here‚ and you’re still complaining?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 133.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね。そんな時間ないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. There’s not much time to waste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 138.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "後悔……しなかったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t… regret it‚ did you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、そのこと気にしていたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it. You were worried about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 145.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "うん、{user}くんに\n一緒に来て手伝ってって言った時に、決心したから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. {user}‚\nwhen you told me you’d come with me to help out‚ I promised myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリで優勝して\n必ず、凄いアイドルになる……",
      "translations": {
